CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 26, 1962, pg. 29 reads: "24th Anniversary - Dr. and Mrs. Porter W. Phillips recently celebrated their 24th anniversary at Carrone Baptist Church. Leading local pastors wre presented in a week of service which culminated in a banquet in the dining room of the church.  Left to right, seated: The Rev. and Mrs. William Ettinger, Mrs. J.M. Finley Brown, William Brown, Dr. Brown, Mrs. Phillips and Dr. Phillips, the honorees; Mrs. Walter A. Linaberge and the Rev. Mr. Linaberger, John Writt, Ruth Ann Bell and Edith Bell.  Standing: The Rev. and Mrs. Arthaniel Harris, the Rev. and Mrs. Eugenia L. Roberts, Dr. and Mrs. Clarence A. Burrell. Mrs. Leroy Patrick, the Rev. Mr. Patrick, Mrs. Robert E. Bell Jr., holding Margaret and Bobby Bell. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, seated from left: Rev. and Mrs. William Ettinger, Mrs. J.M. Finley Brown, William Brown, Dr. Brown, Mrs. and Dr. Porter W. Phillips, Mrs. and Rev. Walter A.
